('00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', '01129498_Afan_Oromo_Truth.txt', 'Kabajama ,gargaara koo akami nagaa Jirtanu? Anif matiin  koo hundinu galata waqayyoo naga jiru. Hallii qilleensaa naannoo kenya bayye namat tola  biyyi tenya Itoophiyaan sirna  mata  of danda’ee qabdi kesumatuu Oromiyaa sirnaa abba gadaatiin bulti sirnii abba gada kuniilee wagga saddeetti  saddeetiin waliif  dabarse kenna. 
