01187498', 'Dear Mr.  & Mrs. Gillian & Brady Shanks,
Greetings to you!
I am your beloved sponsor child Saaritha, very happy to write to you. I am doing good and hope you are doing good.

I go to school every day. I participated in a dance competition held during a cultural program at our school and performed a dance.During the summer holidays, I went to my grandmother’s house. There was a mango orchard there, so I ate a lot of mangoes.

In our village, the Vinayagar Chaturthi festival was celebrated with great enthusiasm. On that day, my mother prepared offerings and placed them before the deity. The idol of Lord Vinayagar was brought in a grand procession. We were all very happy that day.

We have a guava tree in our house, and it is bearing many fruits now. During the quarterly holidays, I went to my aunt''s village, where a temple festival was held. I participated in it, danced, and felt very happy.

For the upcoming Diwali festival, my father has promised to buy me new dress, sweets, and fireworks. During Deepavali nights, I will burst a lot of crackers.I received the CDG you sent me and it has been very helpful to me.

On my birthday, all our family members went to the temple together. At home, my mother made payasam (a sweet dish) for me, and I shared it with my friends.I regularly attend the Creative Learning Centre (CLC) and They are very helpful for my studies.

Preparations are going on for the upcoming Children''s Day celebrations in our village, and arrangements are being made to celebrate it joyfully.There are also efforts underway to declare our village as a "Child Marriage Free Village," which makes me very happy.

Thank you so much for selecting me as your sponsor child and for your care and affection towards me. I pray for your good health and well-being daily.
Thanking you
With love,
Saaritha Dass', '(ind) Tamil', 'English', true),
('00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', '01189291_Tamil_Truth.txt', 'அன்புள்ள திருமதி. Kalpna Goel,
